<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="attention-n">attention <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'tenʃn/    美 /ə'tenʃn/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>注意；专心：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>May / Could I <strong>have your attention</strong>, please?
请注意!</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>turned</strong> his <strong>attention</strong> back <strong>to</strong> the road again.
他把注意力又转回到道路上。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>兴趣；关注：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The post has since gained the attention of social media users all over the world.
之后，这个帖子得到了世界各地社交媒体用户的关注。</p><footer>2018 全国</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Rob loves being <strong>the centre of attention</strong>.
罗布喜欢成为人们关注的焦点。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>关心；照料：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Thank you for your kind attention. 
谢谢你善意的关心。</p><footer>译林③ – 3</footer></div>

<h4 id="4">4.<strong>维修；保养：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The old car <strong>needs</strong> a lot of <strong>attention</strong>.
这辆旧车该大修了。</p></div>

<h4 id="5">5.<strong>立正姿势：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Attention</strong>!
立正！</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They are <strong>standing at attention</strong>.
他们在立正站着。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="attract-catch-get-the-attention-of">attract / catch / get the attention of …</h3>
<p>1.<strong>吸引 / 引起 / 得到……的注意：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She waved to attract the attention of the waitress.
她挥手想引起服务员的注意。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The excellent football player quickly caught the attention of the public.
这个出色的足球运动员很快就吸引了公众的注意。</p></div>

<h3 id="bring-sth-to-sbs-attention">bring sth to sb’s attention</h3>
<p>1.<strong>使某事引起某人的 注意：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Why don't you bring it to his attention that you're too ill to work on?
你为什么不告诉他你病得很厉害，不能继续工作呢？</p><footer>2011 江西</footer></div>

<h3 id="call-draw-attention-to">call / draw attention to</h3>
<p>1.<strong>使人们关注：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The purpose of the campaign is to draw public attention to the needs of the tall.
这项活动的目的是让公众关注高个子人群的需求。</p><footer>2011 全国改</footer></div>

<h3 id="hold-keep-sbs-attention">hold / keep sb’s attention</h3>
<p>1.<strong>保持某人的注意力：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>This game is fun and is sure to keep children's attention.
这个游戏很有趣，一定能保持孩子们的注意力。</p></div>

<h3 id="pay-attention-to">pay attention to</h3>
<p>1.<strong>注意：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>On the bus, you will often notice someone paying more attention to his mobile phone.
在公共汽车上，你常会看到有人更专注于看自己的手机。</p><footer>2013 安徽改</footer></div>

<h3 id="with-attention">with attention</h3>
<p>1.<strong>专心致志地：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The lawyer listened with full attention, trying not to miss any point.
这位律师全神贯注地听着，竭力不漏掉任何要点。</p><footer>2010 四川</footer></div></div>